{"tid":1563110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知道大家見美國肯幫手係開心嘅　但係","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:57:46.000Z","uid":309496,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30f4e5572b8f9652544ab05789f55c934398867a","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"記唔記得14年後期有大量革命衍生作品（歌、圖、商品等等）hit起？<br />\n嗰陣時個個都好開心咁share呢啲作品嚟放鬆連日嚟積累嘅壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然，人長期處於緊張狀態分分鐘搞到神經衰弱，偶爾放鬆一日兩日，一齊唱下歌，振奮下士氣都無壞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係！我哋未贏！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日有人發現：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>據聞美國只需一位參議員提出senate hold，只要全體不足三分二反對，香港人權及民主法案即可在參議會上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無限期擱置</span></span></strong>，直至有關議員收回動議。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢場戰爭一開頭，我哋時常提醒自己唔可以重蹈覆轍、唔好膠化場革命、唔准食人血饅頭&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n時間一長，呢一個星期內，唔知係唔係因為開學，好多學生焗住轉移戰場去返自己學校，於是令大家感覺大街上嘅戰鬥場面少咗；加上美國嗰邊又有好大呼聲話要支援我哋，就咁樣我哋鬆懈咗&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我喺屋企嗰頭嗌口號都無人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記住！美國國會一日未過《香港人權及民主法案》、侵侵一日未簽定作實，我哋都仲只係俾人撳住嚟打！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過當然，街頭少咗人，我哋唔應該喺不必要嘅時候同對方打；我哋可以<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">簽下聯署</span></strong>、<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>心心同retweet下香港新聞</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">罷食罷買罷搭</span></strong>，再等到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">週末出去一齊行</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次出po，寫得唔好多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0637ab86cdd76dbe440304e3193b7ab8f79861d","tid":1563110,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3b8988f9b543c4aba1daa5992b3389e512556c8f","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"真係好驚返返去14年嗰陣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059de4aa4e4925e64e255ed50eb72d32e641a04f","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1/10"},{"pid":"3d61a01423ad5cc5619aa364c58522e44f3ec273","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"自推十連 2/10"},{"pid":"17a59718b87036cb32c9b054fac50b5df2cb5f3c","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連 3/10"},{"pid":"9a74254653ecdd5c55d8122a8e0ecf385b4c7a71","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 4/10"},{"pid":"56a2ca236aac7f301b58f88237fa3fbb9206bede","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連 5/10"},{"pid":"fe1931fdf72910a7d389a6d28141c82dcc04b1b9","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"自推十連 6/10"},{"pid":"8cca72c3c75755a3ac7ce38063be252b4682d36f","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"自推十連 7/10"},{"pid":"a6f50adfccee246b633fc441086d1de3c9f5764a","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"自推十連 8/10"},{"pid":"f4b9018736e1344898d6b138209eb1f028191926","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 9/10"},{"pid":"99817c442d0b4601897beef3d7d13275b1b13e4d","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"自推十連 10/10"},{"pid":"4d80c0d2253089bd83694e52c24778b4055e2ac0","tid":1563110,"uid":93311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8988f9b543c4aba1daa5992b3389e512556c8f","tid":1563110,"uid":309496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"真係好驚返返去14年嗰陣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}